Global Near Infrared Medical Imaging Market Insights
Near Infrared Medical Imaging Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.6 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Near Infrared Medical Imaging Market Overview
The Near Infrared Medical Imaging Market is projected to reach USD 2.1 billion by 2027, growing at a CAGR of 9.3% during the forecast period. This technology is used primarily for non-invasive imaging of tissues and organs, offering several advantages, including high resolution, safety, and the ability to visualize tissues in real-time. The growing prevalence of chronic diseases, rising demand for early diagnosis, and advancements in imaging technologies are expected to drive the market growth. With a wide range of applications in neurology, oncology, and cardiology, the market is experiencing increasing adoption, especially in emerging economies.

